data.description: If you’re looking for a spacious home with plenty of bedrooms and room for entertainment, look no further. The main floor features a Bedroom with Bathroom that could be used as a Master. The open concept kitchen flows into the living room area as well as an elevated back deck that overlooks the private wooded area behind the home. As you reach the upstairs area, you’ll find another large open area for relaxing with a 16X20 Loft area. The impressive 21X14 Master Suite offers a large walk-in closet, double sinks, a large garden tub plus a shower. There are 3 other generous sized rooms on the upstairs level as well as a large walk-in laundry room. The finished basement offers a large 25X19 space that could be used as a billiards room, movie room or general entertainment. There is a 6th Bedroom and full bath located downstairs as well as a 12x11 unfinished room for storage. Walking out of the basement level you’ll find a full-length 36X16 patio with plenty of room for outside activities. The owners also installed a 3rd parking pad for additional parking. This home is conveniently located to all the conveniences of Five Forks and just 2 miles from the Mesa Soccer Complex. The neighborhood features a pool as well as sidewalks.
